Package: CrossClustering
Type: Package
Title: A partial clustering algorithm with automatic estimation of the
       number of clusters and identification of outliers for spherical or
       elongated clusters, with two tests for the significance of the 
       adjusted Rand Index and the computation of it and its confidence 
       interval from contingency tables 
Version: 3.3.01
Date: 2018-02-12
